  "keyFeatures": [
    "JWT Bearer authentication with role-based authorization (SUPER_ADMIN, ADMIN_GENERAL, GESTOR_SUPREMO, GESTOR, CUSTOMER)",
    "Multi-tenant architecture with per-company data isolation via CompanyID claim",
    "Full service catalog management with activation/deactivation and logical deletion",
    "Service request lifecycle: creation, payment proof upload, manual payment validation, status transitions, and refund confirmation",
    "Custom (uncatalogued) service request pipeline for ad-hoc service inquiries",
    "File upload support for payment proofs, optional attachments, invoices, and delivery documents",
    "OTP-based password reset flow with configurable expiration and rate limiting",
    "Dual audit trail: legacy audit logs and a structured AuditEvents/AuditChanges PRO system",
    "System diagnostics endpoints (status, metrics, resources, recent errors) restricted to SUPER_ADMIN",
    "Middleware stack: correlation ID tracking, structured request logging, and JSON error normalization"
  ],
